Bxd4 Bc6 12. Bf3 a5 {- Game 5} (12... Nd7 {- Game 6}))) (9... Ng4 {- Game 10})
(9... Qb6 {- Game 12}) (9... e5 {- Game 13}) (9... Nxd4 {- Game 14}) 10. Nxc6
