Rc8 Rxc8 20. Qxc8 {wins by pin;}) ({while if} 18... Rb7 19. e4 $1 (19. Rc8 {is
not so good here because of} Rxc8 20. Qxc8 Qxc8 21. Rxc8 b4 {and Black has
counterplay}) 19... Bxc5 20. Bxc5 Bc4 21. Nxc4 bxc4 22. Qxc4 {and White, with
