) ({Better is the critical} 10... Bg4 {, which I will examine in the next game.
}) 11. Rd1 Nc6 12. Bb2 {Not a very active square, but where else to put it?} ({
On} 12. Ba3 Na5 {the pawn at c5 is a solid barrier.}) 12... Bb7 13. e4 Na5 14.
Bd3 e6 15. Rac1 Rfd8 16. Qe3 Rac8 17. h4 {Both sides have developed reasonably;
