Black to avoid the Keres tabiya which occurred after the moves} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4
g6 3. Nc3 d5 4. Nf3 Bg7 5. e3 O-O 6. cxd5 Nxd5 7. Bc4 Nxc3 8. bxc3 c5 {. The
