especially considering the inactivity of his normally dangerous Grünfeld
bishop. --- I must mention, aside, that it is much easier to see how these
themes repeat when writing (or reading) an opening book than it is at the
board. But one should try to keep ideas, not just memorized moves, in the
forefront of one's brain!} Rd6 23. Rac1 Re8 24. a4 Nd7 25. b4 c6 26. Ne6 {Just
